<p style="text-align: center;"><span>......</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">气温骤降</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">又到了乱穿衣服的季</span></strong></span><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">节</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">大街上有穿短袖的</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">也有穿羽绒服大衣外套的</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201130/cc6437da418345edbfa02ce0fae88f56.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">厦门广电拍客/M·cheng</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201130/0c7dba26b16a4b5990acad655f65c23a.png" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201130/afb42b8bcb194016a68e9a1ef391a17e.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
